title: Master Lock Bike Lock Cable, Combination Bicycle Lock, Cable Lock for Outdoor Equipment, Black
description: The Master Lock 8143D Preset Combination Cable Lock is 4 ft. (1.2 m) long and features a 5/16 in. (8 mm) diameter braided steel for maximum strength and flexibility. The protective vinyl coating protects against scratches. The 4 dial combination security offers keyless convenience. The Lifetime Guarantee provides peace of mind from a brand you know and can trust.
